{"id":544017,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/【立此存照】外经贸校友车祸事件：删帖、通报、/","date":"2016-11-04T09:31:37Z","modified":"2016-11-05T08:04:17Z","title":"【立此存照】外经贸校友车祸事件：删帖、通报、副区长","content":"<p>2016年10月26日，对外经济贸易大学国际商学院2011届校友丁莹在北京朝阳区北苑路一斑马线行走过程中，因被一辆奥迪车超速导致的7车连环相撞殃及，当天下午<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/%e8%b4%b8%e5%a4%a7%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e6%b1%87%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%81%e8%8e%b9%e6%a0%a1%e5%8f%8b%e8%bd%a6%e7%a5%b8%e4%ba%8b%e6%95%85%e6%83%85%e5%86%b5%e8%af%b4%e6%98%8e/\" target=\"_blank\">抢救无效身亡</a>。</p>\n<p>2016年10月30日，央视新闻曾<a href=\"http://news.cctv.com/2016/10/30/ARTI5HNNIS6qQ3Ji6FHWaizj161030.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">报道过</a>这桩一死四伤的车祸，并播出了肇事司机练某表示悔恨的画面。</p>\n<p>在许多外经贸校友的努力下，丁莹的遇难获得了大量网民的关注。与此同时，相关内容却也在网上遭到了大面积删除，微信、微博、知乎等平台无一幸免。更有知乎用户称其发表的内容遭到网信办定点删除。</p>\n<p>中国数字时代昨日转自微信公号“贸大金融汇”的《<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/%e8%b4%b8%e5%a4%a7%e9%87%91%e8%9e%8d%e6%b1%87%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%81%e8%8e%b9%e6%a0%a1%e5%8f%8b%e8%bd%a6%e7%a5%b8%e4%ba%8b%e6%95%85%e6%83%85%e5%86%b5%e8%af%b4%e6%98%8e/\" target=\"_blank\">丁莹校友车祸事故情况说明</a>》，其原文也已被和谐。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_544038\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/微博搜索吴向阳.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-544038\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/微博搜索吴向阳.jpg\" alt=\"%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e6%90%9c%e7%b4%a2%e5%90%b4%e5%90%91%e9%98%b3\" width=\"525\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/微博搜索吴向阳.jpg 1546w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/微博搜索吴向阳-300x158.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/微博搜索吴向阳-768x404.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/微博搜索吴向阳-1024x539.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">新浪微博搜索截图</span></p></div>\n<p>许多网民表示，无法理解这桩车祸何以敏感到被大量删帖的程度。同时，网络上流传着一张肇事车主的登记信息，显示该车主名为<strong>吴向阳</strong>，与北京市西城区副区长同名同姓。有网民爆料称，该车主的车辆登记信息中的联系电话并非其本人号码，而是属于一名叫“练维宾”的男子（下附图）。</p>\n<p>2016年11月4日，@平安北京 终于对此事件作出“<a href=\"http://weibo.com/1288915263/EfZuHhAmq\" target=\"_blank\">情况通报</a>”，称<strong>肇事车辆登记车主为“吴某某”，但与肇事司机非同一人</strong>，“交管部门正在开展进行调查工作”，<strong>事故责任尚未认定</strong>。北京公安官方微博同时<strong>指责“有人散布谣言”，但并未说明“谣言”的具体内容，也未针对任何“谣言”进行辟谣。</strong></p>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>以下图片由中国数字时代编辑收集自网络：</strong></span></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_544032\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-544032\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427.jpg\" alt=\"006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427\" width=\"600\" height=\"299\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427.jpg 1092w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427-300x150.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427-768x383.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrgbdpj30uc0f5427-1024x511.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">网络流传的肇事车主登记信息；微博图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_544033\" style=\"width: 360px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrx9iaj30ku112acx.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-544033\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrx9iaj30ku112acx.jpg\" alt=\"006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrx9iaj30ku112acx\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrx9iaj30ku112acx.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrx9iaj30ku112acx-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wrx9iaj30ku112acx-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">有网民搜索了吴向阳车辆登记信息中的联系电话，称号码属于一名叫练维宾的男子；微博图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_544031\" style=\"width: 360px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wqsme1j30ku11240j.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-544031\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wqsme1j30ku11240j.jpg\" alt=\"006s1pa2jw1f9g4wqsme1j30ku11240j\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wqsme1j30ku11240j.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wqsme1j30ku11240j-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006s1pa2jw1f9g4wqsme1j30ku11240j-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博图片</span></p></div>\n<p>知乎相关提问被删：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_544018\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/6aa4e8dajw1f9fu5x2sofj20hs0fe401.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-544018\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/6aa4e8dajw1f9fu5x2sofj20hs0fe401.jpg\" alt=\"6aa4e8dajw1f9fu5x2sofj20hs0fe401\" width=\"400\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/6aa4e8dajw1f9fu5x2sofj20hs0fe401.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/6aa4e8dajw1f9fu5x2sofj20hs0fe401-300x260.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">知乎相关提问被删；图片来自新浪微博</span></p></div>\n<p>此微博已被删除：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_544024\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/定点删除.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-544024\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/定点删除.jpg\" alt=\"%e5%ae%9a%e7%82%b9%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4\" width=\"500\" height=\"596\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/定点删除.jpg 952w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/定点删除-252x300.jpg 252w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/定点删除-768x915.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/定点删除-860x1024.jpg 860w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">被删微博截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p>@哥谭有只小猫啊：：还记得前两天刷屏的北苑车祸吗 逝去的那个美漫圈的妹子是我在对外经贸同学的学姐 今天朋友圈看到她发 刚才她说又被删了 究竟在隐藏啥？？？图5是同学发给我的 图6是真相 无关乎隐私 还原事件真相是对逝者及其亲属最起码的慰藉吧 各大社交平台网信办定点删除是几个意思？？？<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7oo0iiwj30ku1127bf.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544020\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7oo0iiwj30ku1127bf.jpg\" alt=\"006rr2oxgw1f9f7oo0iiwj30ku1127bf\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7oo0iiwj30ku1127bf.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7oo0iiwj30ku1127bf-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7oo0iiwj30ku1127bf-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7one59bj30hw067wf7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544019\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7one59bj30hw067wf7.jpg\" alt=\"006rr2oxgw1f9f7one59bj30hw067wf7\" width=\"350\" height=\"121\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7one59bj30hw067wf7.jpg 644w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f7one59bj30hw067wf7-300x104.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pj1h54j30hs1t4wo1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544021\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pj1h54j30hs1t4wo1.jpg\" alt=\"006rr2oxgw1f9f8pj1h54j30hs1t4wo1\" width=\"350\" height=\"1282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pj1h54j30hs1t4wo1.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pj1h54j30hs1t4wo1-82x300.jpg 82w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pjj1nzj30ku112t9t.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544022\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pjj1nzj30ku112t9t.jpg\" alt=\"006rr2oxgw1f9f8pjj1nzj30ku112t9t\" width=\"350\" height=\"622\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pjj1nzj30ku112t9t.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pjj1nzj30ku112t9t-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pjj1nzj30ku112t9t-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pk023bj30ch0m8wjb.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544023\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pk023bj30ch0m8wjb.jpg\" alt=\"006rr2oxgw1f9f8pk023bj30ch0m8wjb\" width=\"350\" height=\"624\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pk023bj30ch0m8wjb.jpg 449w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/006rr2oxgw1f9f8pk023bj30ch0m8wjb-168x300.jpg 168w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>认证账号 @对外经济贸易大学微校园 的文章在其不知情的情况下，被微博设置为仅自己可见：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/2241178205?refer_flag=1005055013_\" target=\"_blank\">@对外经济贸易大学微校园</a>：喔为什么你们都看不到我发的文章了哦我寄几可以看到呀<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/emimage/ee88b1.png\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" /></p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_544025\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/对外经济贸易大学微校园.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-544025\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/对外经济贸易大学微校园.png\" alt=\"%e5%af%b9%e5%a4%96%e7%bb%8f%e6%b5%8e%e8%b4%b8%e6%98%93%e5%a4%a7%e5%ad%a6%e5%be%ae%e6%a0%a1%e5%9b%ad\" width=\"500\" height=\"2765\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/对外经济贸易大学微校园.png 601w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/对外经济贸易大学微校园-54x300.png 54w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/对外经济贸易大学微校园-185x1024.png 185w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@对外经济贸易大学微校园 微博截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[31958,18820,9262,10782,14123,14693,8616,9212]}